
<div class="main_about">
    <div class="ls_help">

        <!--left-->
        <div class="ls_help_lf">
            @Html.Partial("_aboutLeft")
        </div>

        <!--right-->
        <div class="ls_help_rg">
            <div class="ls_help_rg_tit">
                <div class="title1">
                    購物流程
                </div>
                <div class="title2">
                    輕鬆購物7步驟流程
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ls_help_rg_nr">
                <div class="help_bt">1.註冊成為會員</div>
                <div class="help_nr">點擊網頁左上角【註冊】<p>按照網頁提示，完成註冊</p></div>
                <div class="help_bt">2.登入</div>
                <div class="help_nr">在官網首頁左上角點擊【登入】，登入香港惠卡商城</div>
                <div class="help_bt">3.查找商品</div>
                <div class="help_nr">分類瀏覽或直接搜尋來查找商品</div>
                <div class="help_bt">4.放入購物車</div>
                <div class="help_nr">商品放入購買車後去結算或繼續購物</div>
                <div class="help_bt">5.提交訂單</div>
                <div class="help_nr">選擇支付方式後提交訂單</div>
                <div class="help_bt">6.查看訂單狀態</div>
                <div class="help_nr">分別為待發貨及待收貨兩種狀態</div>
                <div class="help_bt">7.收貨後評價</div>
                <div class="help_nr">收貨後可以評價商品</div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
</div>
